title: Day 2 Highlights - 2016 TCT Global Champs | Volcom Surf
description:
DAY 2 HIGHLIGHTS of the 2016 TCT Global Championships! Held at Lower, Trestles from June 14-17, with a live webcast on the final two days.

Volcom's TCT Global Championships
-June 14th-17th, 2016
-Lower Trestles, CA
-$30,000 Prize Purse
-Two Day Live Webcast (June 16 & 17)
-250 Invited qualifiers from around the world (Brazil, Australia, Latin America, Japan, New Zealand, Europe, USA, Indonesia, South Africa, and Puerto Rico.

DIVISIONS
-Pro-Am (20 & Under)
-Juniors (16 & Under)
-Grom (13 & Under )
-Squids (10 & Under)
-Girls (20 & Under)
-Your division is determined by the age you are, as of August 1, 2015.

MUSIC:
Song: “Out The Door"
Artist: Hollow Fortyfives
